{"tid":607130,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"健身問題：你地DOMS(遲發性肌肉痠痛)隔幾耐起？🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻","createTime":"2018-03-27T04:53:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T17:44:11.000Z","uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"db199358bb869e2fb3e68f2a20db33af0dd99616","tid":607130,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T04:53:31.000Z","msg":"我次次都係做完12-24個鐘得少少拉緊feel，去到36個鐘甚至48先真係痛，最痛既時間可以維持1-2日...<br />\n<br />\n我個做法，用背黎做例子，我115磅<br />\n<br />\nChin up-30% body weight 10*4 reps(80%累) ，做得偏快谷力上<br />\n<br />\n窄手lat 25磅 6*4reps，唔算太累，但會離心果下做慢d拎feel<br />\n<br />\nChin up-50% body weight 8*4 reps(80%累)，盡量離心果下慢<br />\n<br />\n 以上動作岩，背肌感受到<br />\n<br />\n然後再hea飛下後膊<br />\n<br />\n做完拉筋都叫有，但唔太多，無特別食咩補品，會食多少少蛋白質<br />\n<br />\n訓覺時間不嬲唔規則唔穩定，有時做完果日都係訓4-5個<br />\n<br />\nDeley咁耐係咪唔正常？"},{"pid":"43418c616a997a43c6708317078736b21c7568d0","tid":607130,"uid":1734,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:03:14.000Z","msg":"115 磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec79c98b382b52bc41c0af29fb75e5c8c7a1a8e","tid":607130,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:03:54.000Z","msg":"不嬲唔會即時 但都唔會太耐"},{"pid":"4bc2aa3fe568503f958cd7e88520b758df7b8c81","tid":607130,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:05:39.000Z","msg":"你玩115磅   定你115磅？？？？<br />\n絲打？"},{"pid":"a2190068c8dae7de70bc1318a4de9a15764e6213","tid":607130,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ec79c98b382b52bc41c0af29fb75e5c8c7a1a8e","tid":607130,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:03:54.000Z","msg":"不嬲唔會即時 但都唔會太耐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:06:51.000Z","msg":"星期六中午做完背，尋日朝先開始痛到7成，夜晚最痛痛到呢架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似太遲發又太耐"},{"pid":"569c5d90efee1fae34d714d88aa178b8664530fd","tid":607130,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu